{
    "text": "\ud83d\udd18Mount Laojun's Temple\ud83d\udd18 \u26abLocated in Henan Province, China. \u26abIt's pavilion with a painted golden roof sits atop one of the peaks of Laojun Mountain.  \u26abLaojun Mountain is known for its cultural heritage of Taoism , the mountain owes its name to the famous philosopher Lao Tzu, founder of Taoism and who resided on the mountain as hermit.  \u26abLaojun is the highest peak of the Funiu Mountains, with a height of 2217m.  \ud83c\udfefFollow me @ancient.scientist to enjoy more and more posts about our world's marvellous History.\u2764  \ud83d\udce9Dm me for Promotion/ Business/ Advertisement\ud83d\udce9  \ud83d\udcf7 Photos by @hwang199 Thank you  #china #laojunshan #laojunmountain #temple #henan #europe #explorepage #explore #instatravel #traveller #wanderlust #travelblog #explorer #travel #nature #travelphotography #traveler #travelpics #video #traveladdict #exploremore #globetrotter #travelbug #traveltheworld #earth #traveling #world #travelphoto",
